      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.Item.MMyeA7kL5Vhcio05]{Nanocyte}</p>\n<p>In certain situations, you can use a nanite surge to push your nanites to perform extraordinary feats a number of times per day equal to half your nanocyte level plus your Constitution modifier; the exact benefits vary by circumstance and are explained in the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.Item.MMyeA7kL5Vhcio05]{Nanocyte} class. At 5th level, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to gain and immediately use an additional nanite surge. You can use this ability multiple times.</p>"
